101-280a @#/ /'phags pa shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa brgyad stong pa'i gzungs / bcom ldan 'das ma yum shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa la phyag 'tshal lo/ /tad+ya thA/ o~M hrIHshru ti smr-i ti bi dza ye swA hA/ pradz+nyA pA ra mi tA ye+e/ sarba durga te shwa d+ha ya/ rA dzA ya swA hA/ 'di bzung bas shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa brgyad stong pa gzung bar 'gyur ro/ /ltas ngan pa sna tshogs kyang zlog go/ /las kyi sgrib pa dang / ngan song thams cad rnam par sbyong bar 'gyur ro/ 'phags pa shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa brgyad stong pa'i gzungs rdzogs so//
